145
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:55,399
No one can threaten me, Leng Qingqiu.

146
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,399
Lu Chengwen,

147
00:05:57,639 --> 00:05:58,600
let's get engaged.

148
00:05:59,480 --> 00:05:59,800
Ah?

149
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,279
I'm willing to be with you.

150
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,199
Young Miss,

151
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:10,639
